{"tid":1163462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(奇文共賞)華為禁令或使 P30、Mate 20 系列聲價十倍！？","createTime":"2019-05-20T12:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T11:24:32.000Z","uid":128859,"like":112,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9a4a75a34dcc827ce04e792b2146522d880280","tid":1163462,"uid":128859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"早前美國政府對大量中國企業實施禁令，只要榜上有名者，美國本土企業將不可以在未得許可之下為其提供任何的軟／硬件技術，而其中，就包括了國產手機龍頭華為 Huawei。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，令手機界熱議，大批華為手機用家都表示擔心現在用的手機會受到影響；然而，Google 方面已經打出強心針，表明現在用戶不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在路透社消息公開後，Google 在短時間內已對傳媒發放了若干聲明，而在最新的聲明當中，Google 方面就指，是次安排僅遵從政府法令，目前有關的後續行動仍然有待進一步商討。<br />\n<br />\n他們在聲明中亦明言：目前已經安裝了 Google 服務的華為手機，將可以繼續得到來自 Google Play 服務以及 Google Play Protect 的保安支援。換言之，近年來熱賣的華為手機系列如 Mate、P 系列的手機將暫時只是未來的 Android 新系統更新受阻，但機照打、Apps 照裝，不過在未來將會推出的華為新機就沒有那麼幸運。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n未及在禁令實施前推出的華為新型摺機 Mate X，恐怕亦成「沒有 Google Play」用的一份子了 <br />\n未及在禁令實施前推出的華為新型摺機 Mate X，恐怕亦成「沒有 Google Play」用的一份子了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若然事態持續，由於沒有得到 Google 的產品使用許可，華為新手機即使可以經 AOSP（Android Open Source Project、即 Android 開源計劃）安裝 Android 系統，仍不可在出廠時安裝任何 Google Service，屆時不單沒有 App Store 進行軟件安裝，亦失去了其他好用功能如自動同步的 Google 聯絡人、日曆等等支援。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新機出廠功能減半，令目前在市場販售的華為旗艦如 Mate 20 Pro、P30 Pro 等機成為「末代」可以用到 Google 服務的華為手機，使它們的價值飛升，短期內在二手市場或會見有一股升浪。</span><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/330871/google-%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E6%88%96%E4%BD%BF-p30-mate-20-%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E8%81%B2%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F330871%2Fgoogle-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BD%25BF-p30-mate-20-%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2580%258D&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=fa47f3d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/330871/google-%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E6%88%96%E4%BD%BF-p30-mate-20-%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E8%81%B2%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n支共01你真係好撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都比你叫人去覺得有得抄<br />\n大家一齊發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c694e44378cd46c62043729c621eb0701ccc683a","tid":1163462,"uid":229560,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb30a95c00473c4dd30612d6489bbd7a8c99b93","tid":1163462,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aac6b510c1c76845cf242aff61740b3c790db3b","tid":1163462,"uid":128859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:50:29.000Z","msg":"訓身抄機<br />\n上樓不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203247384bd7619b873eb914a4476e502fb87189","tid":1163462,"uid":34213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"廢話連篇"},{"pid":"907d9e8560f08fb65f3b55e47027929c72cb45ca","tid":1163462,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"想諗幾耐先可以將呢件慘事講成好事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f25ed7e1b60a8e041de279a7836eb5367d2bb89","tid":1163462,"uid":15564,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/09/23/261926/wnnp002p02a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u